1:08:00.542 --> 1:08:03.179
If you weren't here,
they'd be dead.

1:08:05.514 --> 1:08:07.216
Take it.

1:08:11.386 --> 1:08:14.590
[Matt shouting, banging]
Let me the fuck out of here!

1:08:17.192 --> 1:08:20.729
Let me out of this fuckin' car.
Unlock this fuckin' door, Joey.

1:08:20.762 --> 1:08:23.666
Unlock the fuckin' door
right now!

1:08:26.234 --> 1:08:30.472
Ma'am, I'm gonna
need your car keys.

1:08:30.505 --> 1:08:31.640
[Matt] Shit!

1:08:34.442 --> 1:08:38.147
All right, Matt,
climb on in.

1:08:38.180 --> 1:08:40.883
Joey, get that rope,
toss it in the hole.

1:08:42.250 --> 1:08:44.186
The cops are gonna kill you!

1:08:44.219 --> 1:08:46.455
I don't see any cops
around here. Do you?

1:08:47.322 --> 1:08:49.525
Joey. Joey, look at me.

1:08:59.534 --> 1:09:00.769
Bang!

1:09:00.802 --> 1:09:02.371
You flinched.

1:09:10.946 --> 1:09:13.849
Get going, Matt. Go on.

1:09:16.284 --> 1:09:18.487
-How do I get down?
-Jump.

1:09:31.600 --> 1:09:33.402
Fuck!

1:09:38.006 --> 1:09:41.277
-Ah! Fuck! [groans]
-[thuds]

1:09:42.777 --> 1:09:45.514
Ow! I hate your guts, Joey!

1:09:45.547 --> 1:09:47.282
[laughs]

1:09:47.315 --> 1:09:49.485
So what do we do now?

1:09:50.452 --> 1:09:52.321
Now?

1:09:52.354 --> 1:09:54.456
Now is your big chance.

1:09:54.489 --> 1:09:57.993
-To do what?
-To show him that things
have changed.

1:09:58.026 --> 1:09:59.928
That you rule the roost now.

1:09:59.961 --> 1:10:01.530
I rule the roost?

1:10:01.563 --> 1:10:03.832
Don't tell me. Tell him.

1:10:07.636 --> 1:10:10.505
-I rule the roost, Matt.
-Like hell you do!

1:10:10.538 --> 1:10:11.907
Come on, louder.

1:10:11.940 --> 1:10:13.508
Put some muscle
behind it, Joey!

1:10:13.541 --> 1:10:16.979
-I rule the roost!
-Go fuck yourself!

1:10:17.012 --> 1:10:18.647
Louder!
He's laughing at you!

1:10:20.582 --> 1:10:22.451
I rule the roost!

1:10:22.484 --> 1:10:24.453
Look at you! You're nobody!

1:10:24.486 --> 1:10:26.989
You're as dumb as a brick
and everybody knows it!

1:10:27.022 --> 1:10:28.890
You're dead meat when I get
out of here. You hear me?

1:10:28.923 --> 1:10:30.626
Tell him things
are different now.

1:10:30.659 --> 1:10:32.527
You're not gonna
eat his shit anymore.

1:10:32.560 --> 1:10:35.998
He's not the boss anymore!
That you're the man now!

1:10:36.031 --> 1:10:39.668
-I'm the man now!
-You're the man now!

1:10:39.701 --> 1:10:43.572
I'm the boss to you!
You're down there!
I'm up here! All right?

1:10:43.605 --> 1:10:45.841
I'm the boss!
[panting]

1:10:48.910 --> 1:10:51.614
[chuckles]

1:10:55.717 --> 1:10:58.520
-Hand that over.
-I like the feel of that.

1:10:58.553 --> 1:11:01.624
Yeah. I thought you would.

1:11:04.559 --> 1:11:06.395
But... [clears throat]

1:11:07.629 --> 1:11:09.365
I got some bad news.

1:11:10.665 --> 1:11:12.000
What?

1:11:12.033 --> 1:11:13.869
There's only one place
for you to go.

1:11:13.902 --> 1:11:15.938
Where?

1:11:19.641 --> 1:11:22.644
Down... down there?

1:11:22.677 --> 1:11:24.313
Where else?

1:11:24.346 --> 1:11:27.383
Ha! Send him down to me!
Yeah, send him down!

1:11:28.750 --> 1:11:30.085
I can't. I can't go
down there.

1:11:30.118 --> 1:11:31.853
He'll kill me.

1:11:31.886 --> 1:11:34.690
Yeah. That's how
it goes sometimes.

1:11:34.723 --> 1:11:39.061
Or else you learn
to stand up to him and fight,

1:11:39.094 --> 1:11:40.996
teach him to respect you.

1:11:41.029 --> 1:11:43.799
But he's all riled up.
You made me say those things.

1:11:43.832 --> 1:11:47.035
No. Those things were
inside of you already.

1:11:47.068 --> 1:11:52.040
I can't go down there.
I won't, I can't,
there's no way.

1:11:52.073 --> 1:11:54.677
Okay. Fair enough.

1:11:56.544 --> 1:11:58.080
-Ah!
-[shouts]

1:12:00.048 --> 1:12:01.383
