1:12:01.416 --> 1:12:03.886
-[grunting]
-Matt!

1:12:19.401 --> 1:12:21.370
[grunting]

1:12:25.940 --> 1:12:29.078
[muffled sounds]

1:12:48.596 --> 1:12:50.532
