1:14:21.890 --> 1:14:23.592
And I saw you shoot those cops.

1:14:24.192 --> 1:14:26.028
I can't let you go.

1:14:28.763 --> 1:14:30.799
I've known men like you.

1:14:31.699 --> 1:14:33.568
Violent men.

1:14:33.601 --> 1:14:35.070
My husband was one of 'em.

1:14:36.304 --> 1:14:39.674
